name: PKAddSecureElementPassError.Code
desc: Error codes for problems that occur when you add a secure element passes.

items.name: case deviceNotReadyError
items.desc: The reader for the pass isn’t ready to start pairing.

items.name: case deviceNotSupportedError
items.desc: The reader for the pass isn’t supported or has an invalid version.

items.name: case invalidConfigurationError
items.desc: The configuration for the pass is invalid for either Wallet or the reader.

items.name: case unavailableError
items.desc: Provisioning for secure element passes isn’t available on the device, or the app is missing the entitlement.

items.name: case userCanceledError
items.desc: The user canceled adding the pass.

items.name: case unknownError
items.desc: The system canceled adding the pass due to an unknown failure.
